When multiple output mode indicators are present, the precedence (highest to lowest) is: (1) --json → JSON mode (ANSI never emitted); (2) --no-color → Plain mode; (3) --color=never → Plain; (4) --color=always → Color with resolved theme; (5) NO_COLOR env var set → Plain; (6) stdout is not a TTY → Plain; (7) default → Color with resolved theme. Theme resolution (see <ref spec="output.custom_theme">custom theme</ref>) is independent of flag precedence and applies only when Color mode is active. See <ref spec="output.json_always_plain">JSON always plain</ref>.